guangdong exports 3.76 billion us dollars worth of high - tech products in first two months
xinhua news agency , guangzhou , march 16 ( reporter chen ji ) the latest statistics show that from january to february this year , the export of new and high - tech products in guangdong province was 3.76 billion us dollars , an increase of 34.8% over the same period last year , accounting for 25.5% of the total export value of the whole province .
the bright spots in the export of new and high - tech products are frequent , and this has made important contributions to the growth of guangdong 's foreign trade .
last year , the export of new and high - tech products in guangdong province was 22.234 billion us dollars , up 31 percent over the same period last year , up 27.2 percentage points over the same period of last year , and the net increase in the export of new and high - tech products was 5.27 billion us dollars , making up for the decrease in the export of traditional labor - intensive products due to the decline in prices .
among the export of new and high - tech products in guangdong , computer and communications technology products outshine others , with a total export volume of 19.14 billion us dollars last year , accounting for 85.9 percent of the province 's total export value of high - tech products .
the main markets for the export of guangdong 's new high level technology products are hong kong , the united states , the european union , and japan .
last year , the total export volume of new and high - tech industrial belts in the pearl river delta reached $ 21.9 billion , accounting for 98.7 percent of the total export volume of new and high - tech products in the whole province .
this leading role is still very prominent this year .
at present , more than 95 percent of the computers are installed in the pearl river delta region , which can provide all computer parts other than cpcom .
fifa to severely punish soccer bookmaking
xinhua news agency , beijing , march 17 , the international football federation ( fifa ) announced here today that in the world cup this year , the law enforcement division will adopt more stringent measures to deal with those players who are making profits by means of deception .
the fifa executive board said in a press release that they would give full support to the judges in strictly enforcing the law , especially those who deceive the audience .
the fifa executive committee also announced some reform measures .
the fifa rules that starting from july 1 this year , the players will not be allowed to write any words on the players ' vest , and the fifa will allow the players to show up in their sports uniforms , but they must be in front of the sports uniforms .
suicide bombing in jerusalem
xinhua news agency , jerusalem , march 17 ( reporter zhong cuihua and nie xiaoyang ) on the afternoon of the 17 th , a man exploded a bomb carrying him by a bus in a residential area in northern jerusalem , killing himself on the spot , while nine others were slightly injured and were sent to hospital for medical treatment .
at present , the police have sealed off the scene of the explosion .
less than two hours ago , a palestinian shooting took place in the northern israeli town of qassam .
according to the latest report , a 16 - year - old israeli girl was killed and at least 12 others were injured .
the gunmen were killed by police .
so far , no organization has claimed responsibility for the attack .
the israeli prime minister 's office condemned the shooting .
israeli prime minister sharon said on the same day that although israel and palestine are currently making cease - fire efforts , the israeli side will respond to any attack .
competition to mark 5 th anniversary of hong kong 's return to china
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , march 18 , this year is the fifth anniversary of hong kong 's return to the motherland , and it is also the first time that china has promulgated and implemented the " code of conduct of state civil servants . " in order to celebrate these two happy events , a public servant painting and painting competition with the theme of " state civil servants -- the people 's public servants " will be carried out in hong kong , macao , and mainland civil servants .
the competition was sponsored by the hong kong wen wei po , the china mayors ' association , and the hong kong cultural and recreational affairs department .
civil servants participating in the competition will create the scenery of various parts of the motherland in the form of chinese paintings , and write poems , and will also use the code of conduct jointly observed by civil servants as the content of the work of calligraphy . they will also encourage civil servants to be honest in performing their official duties , to be diligent and pragmatic , and to fulfill their duties , so as to improve the cultural and professional standards of civil servants .
the competition will highlight the festive atmosphere of the fifth anniversary of hong kong 's return to the motherland and fully demonstrate the artistic charm of chinese painting and painting .
it has been learned that the collection of works for this painting and painting competition will be closed on 20 april 2002 .
the winning entries will be published and distributed on the fifth anniversary of the reunification of hong kong .
african national assembly opposes sanctions against zimbabwe
xinhua news agency , johannesburg , march 18 ( reporter : plateau ) - the general secretary of the south african national congress ( african national assembly ) of the ruling party of south africa ( african national assembly ) , brundtland , criticized the united states , britain , and other western countries here on the 18 th in an attempt to force zimbabwe to act according to the wishes of western countries through sanctions .
in view of the threat posed by western countries to impose sanctions on zimbabwe , moeller told the press : " who should be the leader of zimbabwe is the matter of the zimbabwean people , and it cannot be decided by western countries . "
he pointed out that mutual respect for national sovereignty is an international norm that every country must abide by , and the african national assembly resolutely opposes the sanctions imposed by western countries against a sovereign state .
if the western countries further impose sanctions on zimbabwe , it will not only do nothing but also aggravate social unrest in zimbabwe , he said .
he called on the zimbabwean government and opposition parties to work together to overcome the food shortage and land crisis .
he stressed that only by strengthening unity will it be possible to defeat any attempt to split zimbabwe .
earlier , the african national assembly issued a statement demanding that the international community respect the choice of the zimbabwean people and help them tide over the difficulties .
zimbabwean president robert mugabe was re - elected in the presidential election from march 9 to 11 , but western countries accused the election of being a serious violation of the law and lack of fairness and freedom , and refused to acknowledge the outcome of the election and threatened to impose further sanctions against zimbabwe .
at present , some western countries have announced an end to their economic aid to zimbabwe .
before the election , eu countries had imposed " targeted " sanctions on zimbabwe on the grounds that the zimbabwean government restricted freedom of the press and blocked supervision .
french athletes participating in the disabled winter olympics returned to paris with honors .
xinhua news agency , paris , march 18 ( reporter wang jingcheng ) french athletes who took part in the disabled winter olympics held in the us city of salt lake from march 7 to 16 returned to paris today .
at the charles de gaulle airport , the athletes were warmly welcomed by the french minister of youth and sports , the french minister of family , children and disabled people , and relevant people .
the french team participating in the eighth paralympic games held in the us city of salt lake won 19 medals in this year 's games , among which female athletes won nine medals , including one gold medal , and male athletes won 10 medals , including one gold medal .
this is the best result achieved by the french delegation in the winter olympics .
speaking at the welcoming ceremony , seville said that french athletes have changed their views on them with their special performance , and the french people are grateful for their outstanding contributions to the struggle to change people 's views on the disabled .
in his speech , minister bi fei said that the french government will , as always , continue to support disabled sports .
jordan 's first sunday injury breaks out
xinhua news agency report of march 19 th from washington ( by staff reporter xie peilin ) - " flying man " jordan is expected to recover on sunday at the earliest after receiving the right knees surgery . however , as the regular competition is approaching the end , it seems that washington 's talent team will find it difficult to attack the after - season game .
the coach of the talent team , john collins , revealed today that jordan has now stepped up the heat of the cordon . although he still does not want to appear in denver and salt lake city on wednesday and thursday , he is very likely to go to toronto on sunday to rewear his talent team clothes to challenge the current poor team .
collins said : " he may appear at any time , and all this depends on his feeling .
at present , the focus of his training is on defense , and at the same time , he is also practicing throwing a basket .
he is prepared to increase the intensity of his body to check whether his body is fit .
as far as his knees is concerned , he said that at least 100 percent better than before the surgery . "
jordan scored an average of 243.30 points in this season . he received an operation three weeks ago . during this period , the team won four wins and eight losses .
at present , there are only 15 regular matches , with a total of 31 wins and 36 losses , with the eastern alliance in the 10 th place , and the miami warm - up team in the 10 th place .
the coach naturally hoped that jordan 's return would bring about a leap in the quality of the team and at least be able to win one victory after another within a short period of time , so that the hope of the post - season games would start again .
collins said : " if jordan is not absent due to injury , we can win at least three more games earlier . "
as far as the current situation is concerned , he is fully capable of activating the team in a timely manner . "
south korea to send message to north korea on resumption of talks
xinhua news agency , seoul , march 19 ( reporter zhang li ) according to a report by the south korean united news agency , the south korean government has submitted a request to indonesian president megawati , hoping that she will convey to north korean leader kim chong - il the message that south korean president kim dae - jung hopes to resume south - north korean talks and north korean - us talks as soon as possible .
a person from the rok government said that the information content , including the rok , the united states , and japan , hopes to resolve the issue through dialogue with the dprk , and hopes that the dprk will adopt a positive attitude .
it is reported that indonesian president megawati will visit the dprk from 28 to 30 march and visit the rok from 30 march to 1 april .
the south korean government has conveyed this message to the indonesian side through diplomatic channels .
the south korean government denied the report by japan 's asahi shimbun that megawati would hand over a letter written by kim dae - jung to kim chong - il .
european central bank official says euro zone economy to pick up within this year
xinhua news agency , brussels , march 20 ( reporter wang xingqiao ) - the european central bank 's chief economist , dr. yassin , said here on the 20 th that the euro zone 's economy has walked out of the low ebb and will start to pick up at an accelerated pace this year .
yassin made the above remarks at a hearing held by the european parliament in brussels .
he said that the latest data show that the euro zone economy has picked up slowly at the beginning of this year , and it is expected that the economic recovery rate will accelerate within this year .
it is estimated that the euro zone 's economic growth rate this year will reach the level of 2% to 2.5% .
the economic recovery in the euro zone is mainly attributable to the growth of consumer spending and the current low level of commodity reserves in the euro zone , he said .
with regard to inflation , the overall inflation rate in the euro zone has dropped , and there is no indication that there will be a risk of price instability in the medium - term economic development .
when talking about the current world energy situation , yassin said that the recent rise in the world oil market prices has caused concern among the economic decision - makers of various countries , and the impact of the rising oil prices on the long - term economic trend should not be underestimated .
hong kong police first discover drug trafficking on the internet
xinhua news agency , hong kong , march 21 , the hong kong police have recently discovered that some people have been using the internet to smuggle drugs on the internet .
the narcotics division of the hong kong police force pointed out that this is the first time the hong kong police have discovered and should be taken seriously .
the hong kong police said that in the past year , a total of several cases of hong kong people using the internet to make use of credit card payment to buy ecstasy and other drugs were detected .
drug traffickers bought drugs in thailand and sent them to drug abusers in hong kong .
the chief superintendent of the narcotics bureau of the hong kong police force , mr ip lau - chuen , pointed out that a number of cases detected last year were mainly ordered on the internet with credit cards .
the hong kong police are working with the relevant disciplined services to crack down on this new crime .
at a recent conference on cross - boundary organised crime in hong kong , a responsible person of the united nations international narcotics committee pointed out that the online drug trafficking would be a new challenge for future law enforcement agencies .
last year , the security bureau of the hong kong special administrative region ( hksar ) completed consultation on computer crime and will amend the law to crack down on any act of using computers to commit crimes .
african university students urged not to turn africa into an area on the brink of new technology
xinhua news agency , abidjan , march 21 ( reporter song nan ) at the second forum of african colleges and universities , which opened on the 21st , university students attending the forum called on african youths to actively use high technology in information and communications to meet the challenge of economic globalization , and not to let the african continent become a " marginal region " in the new technology field .
in his speech , the chairman of the meeting held that high and new technology has promoted the development of asian , european , and american countries .
the arrival of the new century has brought many opportunities and challenges to the african continent , and african youths should strive to master new and high technologies and make their own contributions to the better future of africa .
the theme of this year 's forum of african institutions of higher learning is : " new technology , information , and exchanges will bring more opportunities to african talent training . "
during the three - day meeting , experts from more than 10 african institutions of higher learning and enterprises will discuss topics such as " the future and new technological challenges of africa , " " cultural diversity and economic development , " and " opportunities and prospects brought about by e - commerce to africa . "
a large - scale school culture exhibition will also be held during the conference .
indonesia reiterates opposition to foreign military presence
xinhua news agency , jakarta , march 22 ( reporter ma tong yuan ) the indonesian foreign ministry issued a press release on the 22nd , reiterating its opposition to foreign troops ' stationing in this island country .
the indonesian foreign ministry reiterated this stand in response to a report in the " usa today " on 20 march that the united states intends to send troops to indonesia to help crack down on the " al - qaeda " members who fled from afghanistan .
the statement said that the us government has never formally made the above request to the indonesian government , and this can also be confirmed from the us white house and the defense department 's denial of the report .
the communique reiterated that indonesia has pursued a positive and independent foreign policy , and that indonesia has carried out close and beneficial cooperation with the united states and other countries to jointly oppose terrorism , and the indonesian government is willing to continue to strengthen cooperation in this regard .
ukraine condemns u.s. interference in internal affairs
xinhua news agency , kiev , march 22 ( reporter zhang zhiqiang ) - ukrainian president kuchma made a statement to the press on the 22nd on the us house of representatives 's interference in ukraine 's internal affairs , saying that the resolution of the us house of representatives was an unprecedented event and " puzzling " .
on the 20th , the us house of representatives passed a resolution on the upcoming ukrainian parliament election , calling on ukraine to ensure a transparent , free , and just election on the 31 st of this month .
the resolution also pointed out that the ukrainian government should earnestly implement the new parliamentary election law , and the results of the election should indicate whether ukraine will continue to carry out democratic reforms .
kuchma said : " the ukrainian nation is not a soccer that is willfully manipulated by others , and the ukrainian people should have their own dignity . "
at the same time , kuchma also expressed his thanks to the president of the world federation of ukrainian people who is expected to send a letter to the us congress .
it is expected that in the letter , " see what you do . "
i studied at home first , and then went to teach others . "
on the same day , the leader of the ukrainian communist party , simonko , said that the us act is a gross interference in ukraine 's internal affairs and a threat to ukraine 's independence .
the u.s. house of representatives ' one - sided evaluation of the campaign will lead to the polarization of the political forces in ukraine , the leader of the ukrainian coalition social democratic party said .
a spokesman for the ukrainian foreign ministry said today that the election of the supreme legislative body and local legislature is purely the matter of the ukrainian people .
in the final stage of ukraine 's parliamentary election campaign , it is hoped that all countries will adopt a cautious attitude and abide by the norms of international law such as non - interference in internal affairs .
arab countries unanimously oppose us attack on iraq
xinhua news agency , riyadh , march 23 , according to a report by the " riyadh news " on the 23rd , lebanese president lahoud said in an interview with the newspaper 's reporter that although the arab summit has not yet opened , they have taken a unanimous stand on the iraq issue and opposed the us attack on iraq .
lahoud pointed out that no arab country agrees that the united states or its allies should strike at any arab country without proper reasons , and the united states must understand the consequences of such attacks , regardless of the pretext or pretext of the attack .
lahoud believes that cracking down on terrorism or " axis of evil " is an attractive pretext that affects western public opinion , but it is not necessary to engage in criminal activities under such a pretext .
he also urged the united states not to pursue double standards , that is , cracking down on terrorism in one region , but ignoring the national terrorist action taken by israel in another region .
