xinhua news agency , jakarta , april 1 ( reporter ma tong yuan ) - the world ranking of the men 's singles player tao fei is very good for the indonesian team to defend the thompson cup , said the president of the china - java ancient trichet badminton club , ali santo , in the provincial capital of sanbaolung on the 1st .
