germany presents un with berlin wall
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 5 , the german government presented the three walls of the berlin wall , a symbol of the east - west cold war , to the united nations on the 4 th .
the height of the three walls is about 3.6 meters , weighing 2.8 tons , and a man and a woman were dressed in the images of a man and a woman crossing the wall .
three pieces of wall were shipped to new york in october last year to mark the reunification of the two koreas in 1990 .
since the un garden , located on the bank of the east river in new york , has been closed since the " 9.11 " incident , the public is unable to visit it .
un secretary general annan took this opportunity to say that the end of the state of separation between the east and the west shows that " peace is always possible , and even in the middle east . "
he told annan that before the berlin wall was built , many people had such a wall in their hearts .
in the end , the berlin wall became history , and not only the germans benefited from it .
