xinhua news agency report of april 5 th from beijing ( by staff reporter li peng ) - the top - notch microsoft corporation president bill gates was " fooled " by a canadian radio station a few days ago , and was a big joke on the day of the april 5 th festival .
on 1 april , the staff of the radio station in quebec , the republic of canada , the mark - an - man , and the saibastiantan , were contacted by phone , saying that he was canadian prime minister jean chretien and had a 10 - minute close conversation with him .
the topic involved the shortcomings of the world economy and the " windows " operating system , and at the same time , bill gates was invited to visit quebec at an appropriate time .
on the evening of the 2 nd , the radio station broadcast the recording of this speech on the entertainment program , and the following day , at the request of the broad masses of listeners , it again made a repeat .
after the incident , mark - antowan o said that he had never imagined that he would be so easy to get in touch with bill gates , and his assistant did not find and did not expect that this was only a " joke " of a foolish festival .
after learning about the truth of the incident , the microsoft company spokesman said that this radio station had fabricated some documents to make microsoft " firmly believe " that they were the canadian government staff , and warned that the " joke " was a bit big .
