computer crime causes us to lose billions of dollars last year
xinhua news agency , washington , april 7 , the " 2001 computer crime and security investigation " report released by the united states on the 7 th shows that the increasingly rampant computer crime last year caused several billion us dollars in losses to us companies and government departments , a big increase over 2000 .
examples of computer systems in various parts of the united states being attacked by computer viruses , refusal to provide services , and various security loopholes are common .
538 computer security experts from enterprises , government departments , and universities said that us companies and other institutions have to pay a high price for computer crimes every year .
although the exact amount of losses has not yet been confirmed , 35 percent of the departments surveyed admitted that they had suffered losses , with a total value of over $ 37.78 billion , a big increase over the figure of nearly $ 26.56 billion in 2000 .
the report , jointly compiled by the us computer security association and the federal bureau of investigation , did not provide any assessment of the loss of personal users throughout the country .
algeria 's official language confirmed
xinhua news agency , algiers , april 8 ( reporter xu donghua ) at a joint meeting of the two chambers held here on the 8 th , the algerian parliament examined and approved a draft constitutional amendment proposed by president bouteflika , and decided that the berlin dialect is one of the official languages recognized by the constitution .
in his speech at the meeting , albanian prime minister ben vriis pointed out that the adoption of the draft law means that the diversity of the albanian culture has been defined in the form of law , and this will be conducive to strengthening the unity of ethnic groups in albania .
the berlin population , which is a native of the north african region , accounts for about one - sixth of the country 's total population .
after the independence of albania , the constitution stipulates that the arabic language is the only official language , but it is opposed by the berlin people .
in april last year , a serious disturbance broke out in the pajero region , where people live in compact communities in the eastern part of the country .
more than 60 people were killed and more than 2,000 injured in the three - month riot .
the local people have demanded that the constitution define the berlin dialect as an official language of albania .
on 12 march this year , in a televised speech to the whole country , president bouteflika promised to meet the demands of the berlin people through revising the constitution .
