xinhua news agency , beijing , april 13 , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue confirmed here today that a chinese worker was killed in the explosion at a bus station in jerusalem on the afternoon of april 12 , and two chinese workers were injured and one chinese worker was missing .
zhang qiyue said that a suicide bombing occurred at a bus station in downtown jerusalem at around 4 : 00 p.m . on april 12 , killing six people and injuring more than 70 people on the spot .
in the blast , one chinese worker was killed , two chinese workers were injured , and another chinese worker was missing .
she said : after the incident , the chinese embassy in israel attached great importance to the incident and immediately sent people to jerusalem on the same day to identify the victims , to visit the injured , to understand the situation , and to contact the relevant departments to deal with the aftermath of the incident .
the embassy has notified chinese citizens and chinese companies in israel that night to take care of their safety and travel prudently .
she said : the chinese government expresses condolences over the death of the chinese citizens involved in the explosion and expresses sympathy for their families .
the chinese side condemns violent activities aimed at innocent civilians , and strongly calls on both israel and palestine to take practical actions to stop violent confrontation and to calm down the situation as soon as possible so as to avoid causing more casualties among innocent civilians .
zhang qiyue said : the chinese government has once again reminded the israeli citizens and personnel who intend to go to israel to pay attention to safety , travel with caution , and contact their families at home . if an emergency occurs , please contact the chinese embassy in israel in a timely manner .
