according to a report by the syrian news agency , president bashar said during the talks : " the incident in palestine has brought the ( middle east ) peace process to a dead end . if we fail to understand this point , the development of the matter may reach an irreversible level . at that time , we can only wait for another generation of people . "
he pointed out that the peace process can only be discussed after israel withdrew its troops from the occupied palestinian territories and stopped killing the palestinians .
he said : " only when both sides are willing to realize peace can peace be realized . "
he called on the united states to have a clear view of peace in the middle east and play a role in this regard so that relevant un resolutions can be effectively implemented .
on the issue of suicide actions taken by the palestinians , bashar said that these actions are not the root cause of the current incidents in the occupied palestinian territories , but are the consequence and a counterattack against israel 's acts .
he pointed out that the best way is to eliminate the root cause of tension in the palestinian situation .
according to diplomatic sources , during the talks , powell and bashar also discussed the issue of the lebanon - israel border situation .
powell arrived in damascus from beirut at noon on the same day for a short visit to syria .
