the russell 2000 index of smaller companies also fell , with the russell 2000 index of smaller companies rising slightly .
declining issues outnumbered advancers by a 5 - to - 4 margin on the new york stock exchange , with nyse volume falling to 1.22 billion shares from 1.26 billion in the previous session .
