chinese fm spokesman on european parliament report
xinhua news agency , beijing , april 19 , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue today commented on a report passed by the european parliament .
a reporter asked : on 11 april , the plenary session of the european parliament examined and approved the " report of the european parliament on the eu 's strategic document on china . "
what is china 's comment on this ?
zhang qiyue answered : the chinese side has noticed that the european parliament recently passed the report .
the report holds that there are broad common interests between china and europe , and advocates the development of sino - european partnership , the strengthening of bilateral contacts , exchanges , and dialogue , and the expansion of bilateral cooperation in the economic , trade , scientific , technological , educational , and cultural fields .
we welcome the above positive proposals .
however , the report has made many erroneous conclusions that do not conform to objective facts on china 's human rights situation and the taiwan and tibet issues , and seriously interferes in china 's internal affairs . this is unacceptable to the chinese side .
it is hoped that the european parliament will earnestly abide by the one - china principle and do more things that are conducive to the development of bilateral relations , so as not to have a negative impact on sino - european relations .
