xinhua news agency , shijiazhuang , april 20 ( reporter yao yajie ) - the reporter learned from the hebei provincial foreign trade and economic cooperation department that since the beginning of this year , nearly 200 - million enterprises of various types have registered their foreign trade operation rights in the provincial foreign trade and economic cooperation department or have been approved by the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation , which is 2.3 times that of the same period last year .
according to presentations , this time , 39 foreign trade companies of various types have registered , of which 17 are private foreign trade companies .
there are also dozens of commercial , material , supply and marketing cooperatives enterprises and state - owned collective enterprises .
77 private production enterprises have also applied for foreign trade management rights .
the entry of more and more private enterprises into the wto is a new atmosphere for the application for foreign trade management rights .
in july last year , the ministry of foreign trade and economic cooperation further relaxed the conditions and standards for all types of enterprises to operate their own import and export rights , changed from the original examination and approval system to the examination and approval and registration system , and stipulated the implementation of unified standards and management methods for enterprises under various ownership systems , thus promoting the initiative of all types of enterprises to declare their rights .
