one quarter voted against or against the work report
npc deputies still dissatisfied with judicial reform
( reported by zhou ruipeng ) more than one - fourth of the npc deputies voted against the work reports of the supreme people 's court and the supreme people 's procuratorate yesterday , indicating that they are still dissatisfied with the reform achievements of the judicial system and the progress of the building of the rule of law .
however , of the 2,813 deputies attending the closing session of the fifth session of the ninth national people 's congress [ npc ] at the great hall of the people , 2,742 voted for premier zhu rongji 's government work report , and the rate of approval was still as high as 97.5 percent , similar to last year .
all sides expect that zhu rongji , who has openly indicated that he will withdraw , will withdraw from the standing committee of the political bureau of the supreme decision - making body at the 16th cpc national congress to be held this fall .
however , the result of the vote showed that zhu rongji was not cold - shouldered by the npc deputies because he was about to lose his power .
the 10 - and - a - half - day meeting yesterday also passed the 2002 budget of 309.8 billion yuan ( about 66.8 billion singapore dollars ) with a vote of 80.5 percent .
the work report of the standing committee of the national people 's congress [ npc ] delivered by li peng , chairman of the npc standing committee , on the other hand , has met with slightly more votes of opposition and votes of abandonment of power than last year .
the report of the standing committee of the national people 's congress [ npc ] yesterday received 587 votes in favor , 112 votes against , and 114 abstentions .
last year 's report won 582 votes in favor , 85 votes against , and 122 abstentions .
although the reactions of the npc deputies yesterday were slightly better than last year , as many as 28 percent and 27 percent of the npc deputies still voted against the work reports of the supreme people 's court and the supreme people 's procuratorate , and they voted against or abandoned their power .
the work report of xiao yang , president of the supreme people 's court , yesterday won 2,026 votes in favor , 528 votes against , and 299 abstentions .
last year , his report won 553 votes for , 530 votes against , and 306 abstentions .
yesterday , han zhubin , procurator general of the supreme people 's procuratorate , received 2,044 votes in favor , 516 votes against , and 253 abstentions .
last year , his report won 1,873 votes in favor , 584 votes against , and 332 abstentions .
since this year is the last session of the current npc and the npc will be changed next year , the meeting that closed yesterday also voted through the " decision on the number of deputies to the 10th npc and the election issue , " which stipulates that the 10th npc should be elected by the end of january next year .
