( hong kong news ) an informed source of the " two sessions " in beijing disclosed to the " ming pao " that after the national people 's congress [ npc ] and the chinese people 's political consultative conference [ cppcc ] sessions , the reshuffle of local party and government leaders in china will be accelerated .
