according to the report , according to the criteria for the appointment of the cpc central committee , members of the provincial - level party and government leading bodies should generally have a bachelor 's degree or above and a bachelor 's degree .
the central authorities also stipulate that the new provincial party committee secretary is under 59 years old and the provincial governor is under 56 years old .
in addition , in order to strengthen the cpc 's leadership over the people 's congresses at all levels , the chairmen of people 's congresses at all levels will be appointed concurrently by the secretaries of the party committees at the same level .
