new york stocks move higher
( comprehensive ) us consumer confidence and industrial production are rising at the same time , causing the wall street market to become more confident , the three major indexes to rise , and the dow jones industrial and commercial index to enter the fifth week more steadily .
investors believe that with the gradual recovery of the us economy , corporate profits are also expected to pick up , with the world 's largest chain of wal - mart stores and credit card issuers taking the lead in rising the dow jones index , the longest weekly increase since september 2000 .
