serious sandstorms again occur in beijing
( agence france - presse , beijing ) - china 's state media said that serious sandstorms again occurred in beijing yesterday .
although the government has invested a huge amount of money to improve beijing 's environment and prevent the desert from approaching beijing , eliminating the frequent sandstorms every year is still the main difficulty facing beijing municipality , which plans to host the 2008 olympic games .
the china national meteorological bureau predicted that the first sandstorm this year hit beijing last friday , and the cold air from mongolia is expected to cover beijing in the dust storms .
yang weixi ( transliteration ) , chief engineer of the desert control center of the chinese forestry ministry , told the " beijing weekly " : " i dare not say that there will be no sandstorms in 2008 .
what we can do is to control the artificial factors that cause sandstorms and prevent the desertification of the environment . "
he said , however , natural factors such as wind , drought , and desert that exceed people 's control ability have made it impossible for china to avoid sandstorms in the short term .
the chinese government has pledged to invest 56.8 billion yuan ( about 12.376 billion singapore dollars ) from 2002 to 2008 to prevent desertification and reduce sandstorms .
beijing alone will spend about 1 billion yuan ( about 220 million singapore dollars ) this year .
an expert from the chinese academy of forestry said : " the increase in fiscal appropriations will greatly improve the situation . however , it may take several decades to see the results of management . "
after conducting an investigation at the beginning of this year , chinese environmental experts warned that about one - third of china 's territory is now in the desert , which is mainly caused by human economic activities , such as excessive animal husbandry .
the report said that in the first six months of last year , 18 sandstorms occurred in beijing , all from inner mongolia , and 60 percent of the land in inner mongolia was desert .
at the just - concluded npc session this month , deputies from shanghai , beijing , and inner mongolia urged the government to " build a green great wall ( formed by forests ) " to stop the attack of sand storms .
according to a report by the " shanghai star , " xu shiyuan , vice president of the china geographical society , warned that if the government does not take emergency measures , sandstorms may even attack shanghai .
many working cadres found to have fake certificates in china
( hong kong comprehensive news ) in the mainland of china , the employment guidance center for the graduates of guangdong province 's colleges and universities recently verified the academic certificate of 15 officials sent by a certain city in the chaoshan region , and confirmed that seven of them were false certificates on the basis of their eyes .
hong kong newspapers reported that since may last year , the centre has received more than 3,500 certificates and more than 800 certificates of various types of false academic qualifications , with a rate of 23 per cent .
the report said that most of the fake certificates were issued by adult education and self - study examination certificates , of which two - thirds were forged on the street and one - third were issued by regular educational institutions .
the person in charge of the center also disclosed that since the inspection department was in the process of institutional reform at the time of the establishment of the inspection department , most of the units that were sent to the examination were organs and enterprises and institutions , and the proportion of the units that had forged documents was very high , and many of the owners of the false documents were working cadres .
with the approval of relevant departments of the ministry of education , the employment guidance center for graduates of colleges and universities in guangdong province is the only institution in china that has been authorized to carry out the nationwide certificate of higher education .
the responsible person also disclosed that out of consideration of the selection of officials , the state - owned banks at a prefectural - level have sent the diploma of 36 middle - level officials and backbone professional personnel to the examination , and only six of the results are true .
it has been learned that along with the appraisal , many private enterprises have also asked for appraisal , and the main items they have identified are the applicants and new recruits .
the examination department found that many of the college students ' certificates were fake .
last year , a large enterprise set up a branch in a place in the pearl river delta , recruiting a group of university students .
the boss sent more than 30 employees ' academic certificates to the examination and found that 10 of them were false .
in recent years , many institutions in other provinces have set up teaching posts in guangdong province , and they have no qualification to issue a certificate of education , but in order to attract students , they have resorted to fraud , claiming that they are able to issue a certificate of national recognition , and they have produced a batch of false certificates to students upon graduation .
