" sandstorms " have occurred in the whole country of the rok .
according to a test by the korean environment ministry , the amount of small dust in the sky of seoul yesterday afternoon was 17 times that of the normal level , reaching 1,000 micrograms per cubic meter , the highest record in history .
under the influence of the nationwide dust weather , apart from the normal operation of the renchuan international airport , six domestic routes , such as daqiu , weishan , and putian , have been suspended , and passengers of more than 30 flights have changed to other transport means .
in addition , according to an associated press report , the south korean government yesterday ordered kindergartens and primary schools throughout the country to temporarily suspend classes for one day to prevent children from being polluted by air .
so far , there have been three dust storms in seoul , south korea .
the south korean meteorological agency yesterday predicted that " a large number of dust storms in the desert areas such as china and mongolia spread over the northern part of china and passed through south korea by the northwest wind . "
this is enough to destroy medium - sized cities ' small planets passing through the earth .
( florida , melbourne , florida ) a small planet , which is large enough to destroy a medium - sized city , has not been discovered in advance at a distance of 43,000 kilometers from the earth , and astronomers did not know the matter until four days later .
the planet , which is about 50 meters in diameter , comes from the direction of the sun , and it is difficult to discover it .
the planet passed the earth on march 8 , but it was already far away when it was discovered on march 12 .
williams , who is located at the cambridge international astronomical association center , massachusetts , helped determine the position of the planet .
from the angle of astronomy , this small planet is very close to the earth because the moon is 400,000 km away from the earth .
williams told florida 's " today daily " on wednesday : " the key lies in the fact that the star should be detected before the sun is issued . "
only in this way can astronomers determine the orbit of a small planet as soon as possible and predict whether it will crash into the earth .
in 1908 , a big and small star hit the earth and hit a pit 32 kilometers wide in siberia 's forest .
interior minister proves that senior government advisers shot to death by " chili brigade "
( agence france - presse , rome ) - italian interior minister scajola confirmed the day before yesterday that the italian government 's high - ranking adviser , biyaji , was shot to death by an extreme left - wing guerrilla " chili brigade . "
scajola said that two men who shot and killed biya even used a pistol similar to political assassination three years ago .
on the other hand , italian prime minister berlusconi has taken the initiative to invite trade union leaders to return to the negotiating table to discuss his employment reform plan .
the 52 - year - old adviser to the labor department , biyaji , is also an economist and a law professor .
he was shot to death by a motorcycle gunmen when he returned to his home in the northern city of borloya on tuesday night , which shocked the italian political arena .
biya has helped draft a labor reform plan strongly opposed by trade unions and left - wing elements .
they considered that the scheme would make it easier for employers to dismiss workers .
witnesses said that biya was lying in a pool of blood , and the other side was his briefcase .
the home of biya was also found to be engraved with the five - star logo of the red brigade , but it is not clear at this moment when it was engraved .
founded in 1973 , the chili brigade was suspected of being involved in several explosions and assassination activities in italy in the 1970 s and 1980 s , including kidnapping and killing former prime minister moro in 1978 .
chinese engineers sentenced to five years ' imprisonment for illegally obtaining state secrets and offering bribes to chinese engineers
( beijing united states ) the beijing no. 1 intermediate people 's court yesterday sentenced fang fuming , an american chinese engineer , to five years ' imprisonment for illegally obtaining state secrets and offering bribes on behalf of a company .
the case once triggered protests from the united states .
a spokesman for the us embassy in china said that fang fuming will be expelled after the prison term expires .
the prison term will be adjusted according to the time of his imprisonment .
the us embassy sent a diplomat to attend the hearing .
fang fuming 's lawyer said that his party had been in jail for two years , but china said it had not been so long .
xinhua news agency confirmed the verdict .
it said that from 1995 to 1999 , fang fuming obtained 35 documents containing state secrets and took bribes of us $ 240,000 ( now about 45,000 singapore dollars ) from chinese civil servants to assist foreign investors in bidding for china 's power projects .
fang fuming is an electrical engineering adviser to foreign companies in china and other parts of asia .
fang fuming 's lawyer cohen said that fang fuming denied that he had offered bribes and said that he was a victim of the corruption of china 's power officials .
fang fuming was a chinese power official in the past and became a us citizen in 1994 .
in the past two years , a number of us citizens and residents have been accused of violating china 's national security law .
fang fuming 's detention once made sino - us relations tense .
the us government has time and again protested against china 's handling of the fang fu ming case , pointing out that the detention of the authorities has not violated international norms for several months .
fang fuming 's family said that he was treated badly .
his wife and two children are american citizens .
cohen said that fang fuming was detained on 28 february 2000 , but the detention period proposed by the chinese foreign ministry was 28 august 2000 .
china does not want to confirm whether hu jintao will visit the united states according to the original plan .
( beijing comprehensive report ) sino - us relations , which had been heating up because of us president bush 's visit to china , were rapidly cooling down , and china yesterday confirmed the cancellation of the plan for the naval vessel formation to visit the us port this year , and refused to confirm whether state vice president hu jintao would visit the united states as scheduled .
in answering a question at a regular press conference , foreign ministry spokeswoman zhang qiyue said : " as far as i know , the chinese naval vessel formation is preparing to visit foreign countries as planned , and their plan does not include the us port . "
when a reporter asked her twice whether hu jintao 's plan to visit the united states was affected or not , and asked her to clarify whether the earlier reply could be interpreted as that hu jintao 's visit to the united states would be carried out as scheduled in april , zhang qiyue did not want to make more comments or confirm it .
zhang qiyue only repeatedly criticized the us side for " doing a series of things in violation of the three sino - us joint communiques " in a short period of one month after bush 's visit to china , and demanded that the us side " stop using the taiwan issue to interfere in china 's internal affairs . "
on the other hand , in washington , the united states paid no attention to the " cold wind " that china warned sino - us relations , and insisted that the united states would allow taiwan 's defense secretary to attend the " us - taiwan defense summit " in florida .
beijing has repeatedly criticized the united states for issuing a visa to taiwan 's defense minister tang yao - ming earlier this month to attend a meeting sponsored by us arms dealers .
at that time , tang yao - ming also met with two senior us officials .
at the regular news conference , state department spokesman richard boucher was asked by reporters about china 's complaints about this matter , but he clearly and forcefully avoided engaging in a verbal war with china .
he said : " after the talks , our stand is known to all .
you have to ask me every day , i am willing to explain every day , china wants to ask this matter every day , and we are willing to explain it every day . "
he said : " there is no change in our stand . these are normal contacts between us and the taiwan people , and we will continue to do so . "
zhang qiyue also confirmed a russian media report yesterday that chinese president jiang zemin had a telephone conversation with russian president putin at the request of russian president putin the night before , and the two sides mainly exchanged views on the issue of mutually beneficial cooperation between china and russia .
both sides held that the mutually beneficial cooperation between china and russia conforms to the interests of the two countries and the two peoples .
